A '''sclipune''' was a [[Beetle/Legends|beetle]]-like creature used by the [[extragalactic]] [[Yuuzhan Vong]] to store sensitive possessions. It had a shell that split in two, and would only open when an individual tapped in the correct sequence to a fringe of sensory tissue on the sclipune's side. [[Deign Lian]] used one to store a communications [[villip]] secretly linked to [[Tsavong Lah]].<ref name="DT2">''[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide II: Ruin]]''</ref> Another sclipune was in the possession of Yuuzhan Vong [[Executor (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|executor]] [[Nom Anor]] in [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]]; this particular sclipune was used to store keepsakes.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

